metadata.name: PHOENIX OF RENAISSANCE
metadata.description:
This place is inspired by London Bridge - a place I visit very often when I'm on my way to work. 
It gives the feeling of an eternal re-birth and starting a new day to be productive and create art. Phoenix is the perfect representation of that. 
The great revival of art.

Created in CLIP STUDIO PAINT.
Animated in Adobe After Effects.

Collector receives full size of the still image as well as the animation in both MP4 and GIF. (2500 x 3500)
